-of-containers","title":"Deeper understanding of containers"}}},{"node":{"id":"6a014320-400c-5ec5-809c-54c8356245e2","frontmatter":{"path":"/part-3/2-deployment-pipelines","title":"Deployment pipelines"}}},{"node":{"id":"b55b95b6-c4c1-5254-9359-a18ca4c66995","frontmatter":{"path":"/part-3/3-using-non-root-user","title":"Using a non-root user"}}},{"node":{"id":"6a684e19-82ea-5b70-86f5-b4f8cab97a1a","frontmatter":{"path":"/part-3/4-optimizing-the-image-size","title":"Optimizing the image size"}}},{"node":{"id":"4d26c1fb-f1ae-5cfc-8865-bc6cf1bdc70e","frontmatter":{"path":"/part-3/5-multi-host-environments","title":"Multi-host environments"}}},{"node":{"id":"967fdd4f-b6eb-56bd-b1cc-d1289c05d626","frontmatter":{"path":"/part-3/6-end","title":"End"}}}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["3294351120","994120085"]}